name: Bush_Furniture_Somerset_5-Shelf_Bookcase
reviews: This looks nice in the picture, and for less than $$$ I wasn't expecting fabulous quality. But the quality was really, really low - something I would expect from a deep discount store. Thin particleboard, plastic (!!) feet, the backing is thick cardboard. All in all, very disappointing.
description: Display professional credentials and reference tomes in your home or office with this Somerset bookcase from Bush Furniture. Designed to match other items in the Somerset collection, this simple yet elegant bookcase features slightly turned feet for traditional visual appeal and a streamlined design that complements contemporary furniture.Includes one five-shelf bookcasePart of Bush Furniture's Somerset collection for easy coordinationComes in mocha cherry, Hansen cherry and maple cross for simple matchingMade from laminate over engineered wood for strength and durabilityMeasures 29.50 inches wide x 12.81 inches deep x 65.22 inches wide StyleTransitionalMaterialLaminate, MDFTypeBook ShelfAssemblyAssembly RequiredColorRed
